Evolution's long route out of the primordial swamp: A deep look at the Earth's interior: New experiments in molecular architecture. "The earth three billion years ago was very different, humans couldn't have existed as there wasn't enough oxygen to support our biology." Andrew Knoll Harvard University. Presented by Roland Pease. Show less